        <div class="msgSubject">Important - elemental stats determine what shards you get</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-14 23:03:09   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1289797389271076939" id="quote-1289797389271076939" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1289797389271076939" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=219&amp;mid=1289797389271076939&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1289797389271076939&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1289797389271076939" onclick="followToggle('add','1289797389271076939')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
