      <div class="msgContentFrame">This is fairly common knowledge, also as a tip, each zone has a elemental afinity. <br /> <br />earth is the black shroud <br />Fire is thanalan <br />La noscea is wind <br />Coerthas seems to be wind. <br /> <br />(have a current theory that i've had for ages since beta that each zone has minor affinities too that are more strongly affected with completely neutral stats.) In general if you have full fire affinity on shards in thanalan you can only get fire, if you have fire in la noscea, no matter how strong, then you will still see some wind shards getting in every now and then.</div>
