      <div class="msgContentFrame">My fire element was about 80, compared to 13 or what ever the starting stat is before I started reset my points. I was only able to get Fire from Black Shroud, but thats when my fire element stat was way above the others. I thought it was based on the area at the time, then now realize it was based on my elemental stat (and area). I know when I left Black Shroud Gridania area (my home) I almost had 1k fire shards a close second was about 300, which was probably earth now that I think about it. I may have been getting earth early on, but that was before I was paying attention. My other shards were from MOBS, well most of if not all. <br /> <br />I'd be curious to see those people who say that they have gotten Crystals (I think they are actually just thinking shards) if they have a certain elemental stat way higher then the others.  <br /> <br />After I posted this last night I saw a couple posts down, a guide, that mentioned elemental affinity affecting your outcome, lol. Most of what I've gone off of is on Wiki.</div>
